USE CASE: 12 produce a country report containing the following columns: Code, Name, Continent, Region, Population, Capital.

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As the organisation, I would like to be able to produce a country report containing the following columns: Code, Name, Continent, Region, Population, Capital.
Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
Database contains Code, Name, Continent, Region, Population, Capital fields.

Success End Condition
A report is available for the organisation to analyse.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Organisation

Trigger
A request for the data is made


EXTENSIONS
None.
